text: Man. What a game... Congrats <@U026NB2U2>! Another year, another landslide. Marce's top two brackets were in the 98th percentile, and his alma mater won their 5th national championship. Not too shabby. Payment can be found on your desk (less $5 for last place).
thanks, <@U026PLK4S> - It was an amazing championship game. Glad that Duke picked up late in the second half.
Thanks for running a tight operation on the brackets!
